"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"The code attempts to set the x-axis major locator and formatter after setting the x-ticks and x-tick labels. This can lead to unexpected behavior because the locator and formatter may override the previously set ticks and labels. The correct order should be to set the locator and formatter before setting the ticks and labels.\",\n  \"patch\": \"19c19,20\\n< ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(MonthLocator())\\n---\\n> ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(MonthLocator())\\n> ax.xaxis.set_major_formatter(DateFormatter('%Y-%m'))\"\n}"